sarocharu ( english : sir came ) is a 2012 telugu romantic action comedy film directed by parasuram starring ravi teja , kajal aggarwal and richa gangopadhyay in the lead roles .   the film is produced on three angels studio pvt. ltd. banner by priyanka dutt and is presented by vyjayanthi banner .   devi sri prasad scored the soundtrack for the film .   the film was released on 21 december 2012 .   the film was dubbed into tamil as sir vanthara which was released on 27 december 2013 .   the film was also dubbed into hindi as jabardast aashiq .